                           <m:mrow>
                              <m:mtext>max</m:mtext>
                           </m:mrow>
                        </m:msub>
                     </m:math>
                  </fo:wrapper>
are accepted, the average value of the distribution is
<fo:wrapper xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                     <m:math overflow="scroll">
                        <m:munderover accent="true">
                           <m:mo>&#xAF;</m:mo>
                           <m:mi>&#x3BB;</m:mi>
                           <m:mrow/>
                        </m:munderover>
                     </m:math>
                  </fo:wrapper>.
</fo:block>
               <fo:block font-size="10pt" text-indent="1em" space-before.optimum="0pt" space-before.maximum="12pt">A parametric fit to the universal Landau distribution has been performed, with following result:
