Vavilov theory</fo:block>
            
            <fo:block font-size="10pt">Vavilov<fo:basic-link text-decoration="underline" internal-destination="bib-VAVI"> [5]</fo:basic-link> derived a more accurate straggling distribution by introducing the kinematic
limit on the maximum transferable energy in a single collision, rather than using
<fo:wrapper xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
