                        </m:mrow>
                     </m:msub>
                     <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                     <m:mi>&#x221E;</m:mi>
                  </m:math>
               </fo:wrapper>. Now
we can write<fo:basic-link text-decoration="underline" internal-destination="bib-SCH1"> [2]</fo:basic-link>:
