                     <m:mo>&#x2265;</m:mo>
                     <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                     <m:mn>0</m:mn>
                  </m:math>
               </fo:wrapper>
the Vavilov distribution can be replaced by a Gaussian of the form:
            <fotex:eqnarray><fo:wrapper xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                           
