                  </fo:wrapper>
               </fo:block>
               <fo:block font-size="10pt" text-indent="1em" space-before.optimum="0pt" space-before.maximum="12pt">The approximation of equations (<fo:basic-link text-decoration="underline" internal-destination="eq:phys332-1">1</fo:basic-link>), (<fo:basic-link text-decoration="underline" internal-destination="eq:phys332-2">1</fo:basic-link>), (<fo:basic-link text-decoration="underline" internal-destination="eq:phys332-3">1</fo:basic-link>) and (<fo:basic-link text-decoration="underline" internal-destination="eq:phys332-4">1</fo:basic-link>) can be used under the following
conditions:
